snippet.title: Release Trailer - StarRevenge 0.5 - Unused Levels V1.1.1
snippet.description:
[Old hack, go play SR5 instead]
Version 1.1,1 out

Link: https://romhacking.com/hack/star-revenge-05-unused-levels

Note: The red coin star and the star for the metal cap in course 7 both have the wrong star name.

Also the normal overworld system is back with the star select screens.
Yes there are some spelling mistakes, but you don't know how bored I get when I write these.

As evil as I am you will get the credits at the end :P

Any question or Feedback? Post it into the comments and I will answer them - if they are not stupid ^^

If you find bugs then tell me so I can wrote them down here:
- don't die in the first castle section - freez

Music1: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=f-sCk_ttVz4
Music2: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ca6jiAkHsaw
